sub_title: professor of Cardiology Erasmus MC, Rotterdam
summary:
Cardiologist specialised in the care of adult patients with a congenital heart defect requiring complex work-ups. 
Over 25 years of clinical experience and teaching to medical students, residents and physicians all over the world. Published over 450 papers in international journals and supervised > 25 PhD students.
Specialties: -Pregnancy and heart disease, -Aortapathology, -Cardiovascular disease in women, -Endocarditis, -Mechanical heart valve, -Adult Congenital Heart Disease, Sports and cardiovascular disease
Chair of the ESC Working Group on Adult Congenital Heart Disease 2018-2020 and member of 4 different ESC Taskforces for developing guidelines.
